name: 2. SUITed Mr.Bad Trip
description:
Let me introduce you Mr.Bad Trip!

This cute little guy is an impersonification of the absurdity (often) happening in my life. He was born from my brain after being f*cked up by Camus's Sisyphe mythos book.

--> you can deduce I did cut my fingers lately, but not that deep!



Inktober 2021, day two, ink on paper.
